computation of coefficients.  User scheduling.  Cooperation: how can massive arrays cooperate?  Distributed array, or centralised array?  Beamforming vs. spatial multiplexing dilemma: the former mainly
applicable in LOS, the latter requiring channels with many degrees of freedom (not always encountered in practice)  Coexistence with CRAN very challenging because of the extreme data rates in the fronthaul
